Garden Rescue - Series 1, Episode 1



Charlie and the Rich brothers are in York, helping a couple who have spent two years painstakingly renovating their terraced home. With a very small garden full of crazy paving and building materials, Charlie and the boys compete to give it a Â£5,000 facelift, turning into a luxurious haven to relax and entertain in.
